<title>USA: Waxman to buy back $12 mln senior notes.</title>
<headline>Waxman to buy back $12 mln senior notes.</headline>
<dateline>BEDFORD HEIGHTS, Ohio 1997-06-06</dateline>
<text>
<p>Waxman Industries Inc said Friday that it has begun the repurchase of $12.0 million of its 11.125 percent Waxman USA Inc senior notes due 2001, at par value. The purchase offer, said the company, expires July 3, 1997.</p>
<p>Waxman said it intends to redeem the senior notes not tendered in the offer to purchase.</p>
